        <ul>
            <li><code>nmap --script smtp-enum-users</code> — automates VRFY across a wordlist instead of manual checks</li>
            <li><code>enum4linux -a &lt;ip&gt;</code> — dumps SMB users, shares, OS info in one shot</li>
            <li>Run searchsploit immediately after nmap — don't manually explore before checking known exploits</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Alternative root path — Samba usermap_script</h3>
